headline.main: Veteran Sixth Man Crawford Leads Clippers Over Bulls, 101-91
headline.print_headline: Veteran Sixth Man Crawford Leads Clippers Over Bulls, 101-91

lead_paragraph: A rhythm shooter on a team out of sync, Jamal Crawford and the Los Angeles Clippers broke out on Saturday night.
